<i>Oh! thought the violet</i>

14:52.828 --> 14:58.044
<i>How I pine for nature's
beauty to be mine</i>

14:58.815 --> 15:04.279
<i>Oh, if only for a moment</i>

15:04.905 --> 15:08.742
<i>For then my love
might notice me</i>

15:08.825 --> 15:13.288
<i>And on her bosom
fasten me</i>

15:13.747 --> 15:16.124
<i>I wish</i>

15:16.207 --> 15:22.066
<i>I wish if only for
a moment long</i>

15:26.051 --> 15:29.638
<i>But, cruel fate!</i>

15:29.721 --> 15:32.349
<i>The maiden came</i>

15:33.308 --> 15:37.896
<i>Without a glance
